<msauri@ohcmd.com>

[Recently the CDC, on the basis of initial data, revealed a potential mismatch between the H3N2 component of the current seasonal vaccine and early clinical isolates, and predicted that the impending seasonal epidemic may be severe. In the preceding message, Dr Sauri describes some early signs that the CDC prediction may be accurate. ProMED-mail thanks Dr Sauri for communicating this information. - Mod.CP

A HealthMap/ProMED-mail map can be accessed at: https://promedmail.org/promed-post?place=3034923,106.]
